WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.460
Hey, what are you doing? Get off the computer.

2
00:00:01.540 --> 00:00:02.660
I'm downloading a song.

3
00:00:02.740 --> 00:00:04.440
Move your feet, lose your seat.

4
00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:08.800
What's the matter with you two?

5
00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:10.680
Do you know how much this computer costs?

6
00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:12.940
You have the protection plan, right?

7
00:00:13.020 --> 00:00:14.640
I don't have the protection plan.

8
00:00:14.720 --> 00:00:17.420
If I believed in protection plans, neither you would be here.

9
00:00:18.980 --> 00:00:22.060
But you guys are spoiled brats. You take everything for granted.

10
00:00:22.120 --> 00:00:24.820
You guys wouldn't have been able to make it through one week of my childhood.

11
00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:28.520
Oh, please. They wouldn't last one night at my house.

12
00:00:28.980 --> 00:00:30.180
You know what? Let's do it.

13
00:00:30.259 --> 00:00:32.180
You guys are spending the week at Grandma Benny's house.

14
00:00:32.259 --> 00:00:33.760
What?

15
00:00:33.820 --> 00:00:36.620
I use your dad's old room for storage now.

16
00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:38.900
So you kids are gonna sleep on the pull-out couch.

17
00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.120
What time do we have to go to bed?

18
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:42.800
I don't care. I got three basic rules.

19
00:00:42.860 --> 00:00:44.160
Don't drink my beer.

20
00:00:45.460 --> 00:00:46.840
Don't touch my smokes.

21
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:50.140
And don't sneak up on me when I'm sleeping.

22
00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:51.600
I got a gun under my pillow.

23
00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:54.340
And I sleep, oh, not your route.

